/*! \page qmotif-extension.html

\title QMotif Extension
\keyword QMotif

The QMotif Extension assists the migration of old Xt and Motif based
code to the more comfortable Qt toolkit.  This extension replaces the
older Qt Xt/Motif Supprt Extension included with earlier versions of
Qt.

\section1 Information
The QMotif Extension consists of the follow classes:
\list
\i QMotif
\i QMotifWidget
\i QMotifDialog
\i QMotifEventLoop
\endlist

\section1 How-to
   
\list 1
\i Ensure you are using X11R6 and Motif 2.x.
\i Ensure the programs you wish to port are compilable by a C++
compiler, or at least that this is the case for the parts which
need migration.
\endlist

\section1 Known Bugs and Problems

\list
\i This documentation is incomplete and unfinished.
\i QMotifDialog is not completely implemented.
\i QMotifWidget is not tested with an Xt/Motif widget inside a QMainWindow.
\endlist

*/
